Toggle navigation En français Browse Job Listings FAQ Contact Register Log in Log in Forgot password? Library Assistant Douro-Dummer , ON Description Located in the hamlet of Douro, The Douro-Dummer Public Library is the single public library service point for a close-knit community of just over 7, 500 residents, 14 km north east of Peterborough, Ontario. Douro-Dummer Public Library is looking for a self-starting team-player who is able to work independently. The individual must have excellent communication skills and strong technology skills. Customer service and program delivery skills are essential. Preference given to individuals with library training or equivalent experience. Reliable transportation is required. Part time – 15 hours per week (flexible-day, evening, weekend).Position: Library AssistantSalary: Between $23.92 - $26.30 per hourStatus: Permanent/ Part-time - 15 hours per week, some evening and weekend workStart Date: As soon as possiblePosition Summary: Under the direction of the Library CEO, the Library Assistant is responsible for providing excellent customer service to library patrons through a variety of duties including circulation, readers’ advisory, interlibrary loans, programming, outreach, and other tasks as required.View the complete job descriptionQualifications:Must possess one year related experience in library or similar public services; Library Technician diploma is an asset.Must possess a Class “G” driver’s licenseGood organization and communication skillsProven ability to deal with the publicProven ability to use computers, Microsoft Word and Excel, emails; knowledge of an Integrated Library System is an assetKnowledge of Provincial and Municipal legislation pertaining to libraries.Able to work flexible hours, including 1 evening per week (Wednesdays) and/or SaturdaysSuccessful candidate will be required to produce a current Vulnerable Sector CheckInterested applicants are invited to send a cover letter and resume to maggiep@dourodummer.on.ca by Wednesday, March 20th, 2024 at 4pm.We thank all those in advance who apply but only those selected for an interview will be contacted. Compensation Between $23.92 - $26.30 per hour Closes: 20 March, 2024 Douro-Dummer Library Douro-Dummer , ON Policies and Terms of Use · jobboard@bcla.bc.ca / BCLA PO BOX 19008, Rocky Point PO, Port Moody, BC V3H 0J1 window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
